OL,6,FA woman who made her husband's life a
OL,7,F"misery" through an almost daily
OL,8,Fcampaign of abuse and attacks has been
OL,9,Fjailed for coercive control.
OL,11,FHelen Thornton, 45, repeatedly
OL,12,Fattacked the man with a rolling pin
OL,13,Fand on one occasion stabbed him with
OL,14,Fthe sharp point of an electric
OL,15,Ftoothbrush, Hull Crown Court heard..
OL,17,FThornton, of Emfield Road, Grimsby,
OL,18,Fdenied two offences of assault causing
OL,19,Factual bodily harm and another of
OL,20,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour.
