OL,6,FShe was convicted after a trial at
OL,7,FGrimsby Crown Court.
OL,9,FSentencing her, Judge John Thackray KC
OL,10,Fsaid she was guilty of "instilling
OL,11,Ffear" in her husband on at least two
OL,12,Foccasions between 2016 and last year.
OL,14,F"You made his life a misery and it's
OL,15,Fnot less serious because it was
OL,16,Fcommitted in a domestic setting, it's
OL,17,Fmore serious because it involved a
OL,18,Fbreach of trust," he said.
