OL,6,FHe added: "You would shout and abuse
OL,7,Fhim. This is a very serious case of
OL,8,Fits kind. It's not less serious
OL,9,Fbecause you are a female. That doesn't
OL,10,Fmake any difference whatsoever.
OL,12,F"It's persistent behaviour over a long
OL,13,Fperiod and it has had a profound
OL,14,Feffect upon your victim. It took him a
OL,15,Flong time to report you for this
OL,16,Fbehaviour. Eventually, he summoned the
OL,17,Fcourage to report you and he bravely
OL,18,Fgave evidence against you.
